{"start":0,"end":2600,"text":"Hi, how can I help you?"}
{"start":2600,"end":3000,"text":"I'd like to..."}
{"start":2977,"end":5977,"text":"I like to buy flowers for my mum since today is my..."}
{"start":5955,"end":8955,"text":"Mother's Day. In that case, I recommend you to..."}
{"start":8933,"end":11933,"text":"to buy car nations. They are very popular on my own."}
{"start":11911,"end":14911,"text":"I prefer to buy some special food."}
{"start":14889,"end":16889,"text":"Flowers different from others."}
{"start":16889,"end":17889,"text":"No problem."}
{"start":17867,"end":19307,"text":"Do you like lilies?"}
{"start":19307,"end":20827,"text":"Lilies are related to purity."}
{"start":20845,"end":23805,"text":"and virtue. Mmm, it's lovely, could you?"}
{"start":23823,"end":25223,"text":"You helped me wrap them."}
{"start":25223,"end":26223,"text":"Sure."}
{"start":26223,"end":26823,"text":"Would you like a thank you?"}
{"start":26801,"end":29801,"text":"you note with the flowers? Yes, that would be perfect."}
{"start":29779,"end":32579,"text":"your mother's name, Sylvia."}
{"start":32757,"end":34757,"text":"S-I-L-V-I-A."}
{"start":34757,"end":35757,"text":"No, it's S-1."}
{"start":35735,"end":37735,"text":"Y-L-V-I-A."}
{"start":37735,"end":38735,"text":"Okay, would you..."}
{"start":38712,"end":41712,"text":"like to put a sentence. Oh, just I love you."}
{"start":41690,"end":44690,"text":"May I have the address you'd like to deliver them to?"}
{"start":44668,"end":47268,"text":"It's 18 Drake fell road."}
{"start":47646,"end":49646,"text":"Could you tell me how to spell it?"}
{"start":49646,"end":50646,"text":"Yes, D.R."}
{"start":50624,"end":53364,"text":"a K-E-F-E-L-L."}
{"start":53602,"end":56482,"text":"Okay, when do you like the flowers to be delivered?"}
{"start":56580,"end":59580,"text":"Um, probably 10 a.m. Oh my f-"}
{"start":59558,"end":62518,"text":"Forgot we would visit my aunt until 1pm."}
{"start":62536,"end":65536,"text":"Can you deliver them at 3.30pm?"}
{"start":65514,"end":68514,"text":"No problem. The delivery fee is 5 pounds."}
{"start":68492,"end":71012,"text":"It's 25 pounds altogether."}
{"start":71470,"end":74070,"text":"I have given you a discount of 10%."}
{"start":74070,"end":74430,"text":"Well..."}
{"start":74448,"end":76448,"text":"That's great, thank you."}
